library(MASS)
hist(immer$Y1)

hist(immer$Y2)

从直方图来看，两者分布不相同

t.test(immer$Y1,immer$Y2,paired = TRUE)
## 
##  Paired t-test
## 
## data:  immer$Y1 and immer$Y2
## t = 3.324, df = 29, p-value = 0.002413
## alternative hypothesis: true difference in means is not equal to 0
## 95 percent confidence interval:
##   6.121954 25.704713
## sample estimates:
## mean of the differences 
##                15.91333

t检验结果显示，在显著性水平为0.05水平下，可以认为两者有显著差异

x=immer$Y1-immer$Y2
binom.test(sum(x>0),length(x),0.5)
## 
##  Exact binomial test
## 
## data:  sum(x > 0) and length(x)
## number of successes = 24, number of trials = 30, p-value = 0.001431
## alternative hypothesis: true probability of success is not equal to 0.5
## 95 percent confidence interval:
##  0.6143335 0.9228645
## sample estimates:
## probability of success 
##                    0.8

符号检验在显著性水平为0.05的情况下未通过，认为两者有区别

wilcox.test(x)
## Warning in wilcox.test.default(x): cannot compute exact p-value with ties
## 
##  Wilcoxon signed rank test with continuity correction
## 
## data:  x
## V = 368.5, p-value = 0.005318
## alternative hypothesis: true location is not equal to 0

Wilcox符号秩检验在显著性水平为0.05的情况下未通过，认为两者有区别

结论

2

c1=c(91,46,108,99,110,105,191,57,34,81)
c2=c(81,51,63,51,46,45,66,64,90,28)
binom.test(sum(c1-c2>0),length(c1),0.5)
## 
##  Exact binomial test
## 
## data:  sum(c1 - c2 > 0) and length(c1)
## number of successes = 7, number of trials = 10, p-value = 0.3438
## alternative hypothesis: true probability of success is not equal to 0.5
## 95 percent confidence interval:
##  0.3475471 0.9332605
## sample estimates:
## probability of success 
##                    0.7

符号检验的结果显示在显著性水平为0.05的条件下不能拒绝原假设，即认为两者不存在显著性差异

wilcox.test(c1-c2)
## 
##  Wilcoxon signed rank exact test
## 
## data:  c1 - c2
## V = 45, p-value = 0.08398
## alternative hypothesis: true location is not equal to 0

Wilcox符号秩检验的结果显示在显著性水平为0.05的条件下不能拒绝原假设，即认为两者不存在显著性差异，但是P值远小于符号检验的结果，可以认为是发生了较小概率事件或是假设不成立

hist(c1)

hist(c2)

Wilcox符号秩检验效果更好，它能够在显著性水平为0.1的情况下拒绝原假设，不仅考虑到了符号也考虑到了相对大小

3

test=function(x){
  m=median(x)
  cat("median is",m,'\n')
  temp=x-m
  n=length(temp)
  print(binom.test(sum(temp>0),n,p=0.5))
  print(wilcox.test(temp))
}

总结

对于中位数的符号检验，除非出现大量相同数据，否则中位数两边的样本数量差距应该较小，但是符号检验没有考虑到样本离中位数的距离
